    {
      "id": "twilite-not-009",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "🚫 What Twilite Is Not",
      "position": {
        "x": -1179.62695036409,
        "y": 483.83378851968183
      },
      "width": 480,
      "height": 360,
      "color": "#f44336",
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## What Twilite Is *Not*\n\nTwilite is intentionally **not**:\n\n- ❌ An autonomous agent system\n- ❌ A chatbot or conversational UI\n- ❌ A no-code replacement for thinking\n- ❌ A workflow engine that decides for you\n- ❌ A black-box AI controller\n\n---\n\nTwilite does **not**:\n\n- Decide what matters\n- Choose the next task\n- Hide state or reasoning\n- Replace human judgment\n\nIt provides **structure and memory**, not authority.\n\nIf Twilite feels like it is thinking *for* you, something has gone wrong.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
