      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## 📊 Current Graph State\n\nThis graph is the *only* shared context.\n\nIt represents:\n- What exists\n- What is connected\n- What has been decided\n\nThe LLM receives **this**, not a summary.\n\nThe graph **is** the memory.",
