      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# 🧠 Work Modes\n\nThis graph exists to manage **cognitive load**, not tasks.\n\nWhen one mode is depleted, **switch modes** instead of stopping or forcing progress.\n\nProgress is defined as *sustainable movement*, not throughput.",
