    {
      "id": "mode-architecture",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "🏗️ Structural",
      "position": {
        "x": 145.54054859990208,
        "y": 1303.8730349725392
      },
      "width": 480,
      "height": 380,
      "color": "#e91e63",
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## 🏗️ Structural / Architectural\n\n**Load:** Heavy  \n**Purpose:** Define invariants and boundaries\n\n**Examples:**\n- Core vs adapter vs app decisions\n- Refactors that move responsibility\n- Naming things that must last\n- Deciding what must *not* change\n\n**Capacity:** 1–2 decisions per day\n\n**Stop signals:**\n- Head pressure\n- Urge to walk\n- \"I can't hold this anymore\"\n\n➡️ **Stop immediately** and switch modes.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
