    {
      "id": "mode-implementation",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "🛠️ Implementation",
      "position": {
        "x": 745.5405485999021,
        "y": 1303.8730349725392
      },
      "width": 480,
      "height": 380,
      "color": "#3f51b5",
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## 🛠️ Implementation / Coding\n\n**Load:** Focused  \n**Purpose:** Execute already-made decisions\n\n**Examples:**\n- Writing functions\n- Moving code\n- Implementing a known refactor\n- Fixing bounded bugs\n\n**Capacity:** Medium\n\n**Stop signals:**\n- Sloppy code\n- Impatience\n- Tunnel vision\n\n➡️ **Switch modes** when quality drops.",
