      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## 🌐 Externalization / Web\n\n**Load:** Light  \n**Purpose:** Make the project visible and legible\n\n**Examples:**\n- Website (twilite.zone)\n- Canva layouts\n- README / copy\n- Explaining Twilite in words\n\n**Capacity:** High\n\n**Stop signal:**\n- Boredom (not fatigue)\n\n➡️ Ideal after heavy architectural work.",
