      "data": {
        "markdown": "## 🗺️ Planning / Parking\n\n**Load:** Recovery  \n**Purpose:** Relieve pressure without losing progress\n\n**Examples:**\n- TODO graphs\n- Parking future ideas\n- Writing \"later\" notes\n- Cleaning up thoughts\n\n**Capacity:** Very high\n\n**Stop signals:**\n- Calm returns\n- Mental space opens\n\n➡️ This is the *best* way to end a day.",
